      ],
      "text": "General Mak was a general in the Fire Nation military following the Hundred Year War. At the time of the crisis in Yu Dao, he was stationed in the Fire Nation Capital as a military aide to Fire Lord Zuko."
    },
    {
      "body": "After Zuko withdrew from the ${link_0}, he sent spies to the ${link_1}, who reported to General Mak. The spies informed the general that ${link_2} ${link_3}'s forces were marching toward Yu Dao, and he passed this information on to the Fire Lord, which prompted Zuko to sail with a fleet of several ${link_4} toward the ${link_5}.",
      "links": [
        {
